snippet.title: Match Tree - Gameplay
snippet.description:
It's a match tree game. A fresh approach. Meet the Pixie, the Gnome and the Witch and build them homes.

You combine flowers, carrots and trees. 
But be aware of the SHEEP!

Small gameplay lookout of a tiny game I'm tinkering with. Artwort by the awesome @datgestruepp8024 


Available on itch.io as a playable very early version.
https://andi-dev.itch.io/matchtree
